    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      36.47,
      545.89,
      77.35
    ],
    "text": "On 05.06.2026, officers of the Katunayake Police Station conducted three separate raids in the Andiambalama, Katunayake, and Heenatiyana areas within the Katunayake Police Division and arrested three suspects in possession of crystal methamphetamine (\u201cice\u201d).",
    "fonts": [
